{"tid":932542,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]用lan to usb上網upload圖及setting問題","createTime":"2018-12-07T21:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T17:42:01.000Z","uid":138381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1193707548973b02a03839e8dc6c73b9851cbc0b","tid":932542,"uid":138381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T21:26:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟部電腦就用一舊咁嘅lan to usb adapter駁lan線上網<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffpNTHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffpNTHp.jpg&h=5626d064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊野叫 asix ax88179 usb 3.0 to gigabit ethernet adapter<br />\nspeedtest 上傳原本就勁慢永遠唔過1mb,<br />\n上網google disable左Large Send Overload之後數值變返正常<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKDbAXj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKDbAXj.png&h=ddd049bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係唔知點解 永遠upload圖上d up圖網就error 一係就卡住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/qxXf2Eu.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxXf2Eu.png&d=YgRU0upirhQ4ZjU58MBUaI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=532e68d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/qxXf2Eu.png</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/7avEKSP.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7avEKSP.png&d=YgRU0upirhQ4ZjU58MBUaI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2f12379a\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/7avEKSP.png</a><br />\n永遠都要重試好多次先有一次得<br />\n反而用wifi就永遠都一野就成功<br />\n但偏偏wifi個上傳速度又唔夠快<br />\n1. 到底點樣先可以解決呢個問題?定係係果d website server自身問題?<br />\n唔想明明有lan線上網都要專登用wifi黎upload咁白痴...<br />\n2.有冇辦法唔disable large send overload都可以正常上傳速度?<br />\n因為我睇返原port口setting冇disable到試過都行到正常速<br />\n求神人解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa1ed71c78f8c8816323db3ee261b5825bb7569","tid":932542,"uid":138381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T21:28:22.000Z","msg":"題目應該係usb to lan,唔好意思"},{"pid":"63921a004b7c94d098475fc46c45635797705940","tid":932542,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T22:05:39.000Z","msg":"你speedtest連咗咩server <br />\nPing 1ms咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4874793bfa67f421b619cc505d7baea8e9339c","tid":932542,"uid":138381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63921a004b7c94d098475fc46c45635797705940","tid":932542,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T22:05:39.000Z","msg":"你speedtest連咗咩server <br />\nPing 1ms咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T22:25:45.000Z","msg":"VDC 好似係"},{"pid":"f7138264d6a224fb550d6e2b9cb16b1d94cd2b9c","tid":932542,"uid":138381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9807d01190249bdf3493acf2462c2a28c0197622","tid":932542,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"似人哋嗰網問題"}]}